'''Bobolo Baker's All-Bith Band''' was a [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] [[Band/Legends|band]] featuring only [[Bith/Legends|Bith]], founded by [[Bobolo Baker]]. They were popular at [[Nova Station]]'s [[Big Boom]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

